eft" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">What people are saying about our restaurant</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][tm_pb_text admin_label="Text" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_padding="20px||20px|"]\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Anyone, who visits our place leaves us well fed and in a great mood!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="off" parallax_3="off" parallax_method_3="off" column_padding_mobile="on"][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_testimonial admin_label="Testimonial" url_new_window="off" quote_icon="on" use_background_color="off" background_color="#f5f5f5" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" author="Sam" job_title="posted on" company_name="TripAdvisor" font_icon="f10d" portrait_url="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/test1.png" custom_padding="20px|||"]\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">I''ve never tasted a pizza so good before, and this is coming from a New York native! With all of the richness of ingredients and flavors, their pizzas are a perfect treat!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_testimonial][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_testimonial admin_label="Testimonial" url_new_window="off" quote_icon="on" use_background_color="off" background_color="#f5f5f5" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" author="Leah" job_title="posted on" company_name="foursquare" font_icon="f10d" portrait_url="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/test2.png" custom_padding="20px|||"]\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">While I was looking for a nice new pizzeria in the town, I''ve found the best one here! Their pizza variety is ultimate, inferior only to how awesome these pizzas taste!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_testimonial][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type="1_3"][tm_pb_testimonial admin_label="Testimonial" url_new_window="off" quote_icon="on" use_background_color="off" background_color="#f5f5f5" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" author="Alfred" job_title="posted on" company_name="Yelp" font_icon="f10d" portrait_url="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/test3.png" custom_padding="20px|||"]\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">My kids just love the place, dragging me here time and again for a slice of their Spanish pizza. This place has both an outstanding menu and great pricing policy!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_testimonial][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label="Section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" transparent_background="on" allow_player_pause="off" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" padding_mobile="off" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off" custom_padding_last_edited="on|phone"][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" custom_margin="92px|||" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" column_padding_mobile="on" custom_margin_phone="55px|||" custom_margin_last_edited="on|tablet" custom_margin_tablet="70px|||"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_text admin_label="Text" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\