(1229, 1, '2016-05-27 09:00:17', '2016-05-27 09:00:17', '[tm_pb_section admin_label="section" background_image="your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/image35.jpg" transparent_background="off" background_color="#000000" allow_player_pause="off" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" custom_padding="75px||67px|" padding_mobile="on" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off" module_class="invert"][tm_pb_row admin_label="row"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_text admin_label="Text" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][tm_pb_text admin_label="Text" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_margin="11px|||"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nDuring our years of service we''ve noticed that people tend to ask us similar questions.<br />Here we compiled our top 10 most frequently asked requests!</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label="Section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" transparent_background="on" allow_player_pause="off" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" custom_padding="100px||75px|" padding_mobile="on" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off" custom_padding_phone="75px||75px|" custom_padding_last_edited="on|phone"][tm_pb_row admin_label="Row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" use_grid_padding="on" width_unit="on" padding_mobile="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" column_padding_mobile="on" custom_css_main_1="max-width:810px;" module_class="row-xs-flex-center"][tm_pb_column type="4_4"][tm_pb_accordion admin_label="Accordion" use_border_color="off" border_color="#000000" border_style="solid" saved_tabs="all" toggle_font_size_last_edited="on|phone" toggle_letter_spacing_last_edited="on|phone" toggle_line_height_last_edited="on|phone" body_font_size_last_edited="on|phone" body_letter_spacing_last_edited="on|phone" body_line_height_last_edited="on|phone" open_toggle_text_color="#ff8400"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n[tm_pb_accordion_item title="Do you offer vegetarian items on the menu?"]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Sure, we have a variety of vegetable dishes. That list includes salads, garnishes, and main dishes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Does your restaurant have other locations?"]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Currently, we have only one location in Alexandria, VA. But we’re looking into a possibility to expand. Possibly, that might happen in the nearest future.</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="What’s your policy on bringing one''s own alcohol in?"]</p>\r\n<p>We do not encourage this, neither the state legislature of Virginia does….</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="How many tables do you have?"]</p>\r\n<p>We’ve got more than 50 tables in our 2 dining halls, not taking into account the high chairs at the bar desk.</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Do you offer themed parties hosting?"]</p>\r\n<p>Sure! You can book any of our dining halls and host your party there!</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Can I bring my pet in?"]</p>\r\n<p>Unfortunately that’s not possible… However, during the spring and the summer, we have a summer terrace outside the building. Pets are allowed in that area.</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="How often do you update your menu?"]</p>\r\n<p>We do it occasionally. Each new time of the year we add seasonal dishes and few times a year we add themed cuisine (like Italian cuisine days; Ukrainian cuisine week etc…)</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Do you sell cigarettes at your bar?"]</p>\r\n<p>No, we offer only beverages there...</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Do you offer catering services?"]</p>\r\n<p>Absolutely! We have a catering and waiter rental services. You can read more about it in our Services section of the website.</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title="Can you join the tables for me if my party size exceeds 8-guest seats per table?"]</p>\r\n<p>Sure. But we will appreciate if you will book table (s) beforehand in such a case...</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item]</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_accordion][tm_pb_divider admin_label="Divider" color="#f0f0f0" show_divider="on" divider_style="solid" custom_margin="95px||30px|"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label="Text" text_orientation="center" text_font_size="29px" text_text_color="#2b2f3e" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" text_font_size_last_edited="on|phone"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nAny other questions? Please <a href="your_website_url_here/contact-us/">Contact Us</a></p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section]', 'FAQ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2016-12-28 12:21:42', '2016-12-28 12:21:42', '', 0, 'your_website_url_here/?page_id=1229', 0, 'page', '', 0),
